WEBVTT

00:02.163 --> 00:02.828
<i>Previously on Damages:</i>

00:02.896 --> 00:03.564
<i>Josh Reston.</i>

00:03.632 --> 00:04.500
<i>I just got a job</i>

00:04.568 --> 00:05.390
<i>reporting crime at the Manhattan</i>

00:05.458 --> 00:06.308
<i>Observer.</i>

00:06.376 --> 00:07.503
<i>The warmth all lie</i>

00:07.571 --> 00:11.408
<i>behind these walls.</i>

00:11.476 --> 00:13.143
<i>And you two are...</i>

00:13.210 --> 00:14.445
<i>Having a baby.</i>

00:14.512 --> 00:15.713
<i>How much would it take</i>

00:15.781 --> 00:16.949
<i>for you to walk away?</i>

00:17.017 --> 00:18.383
<i>I want you to cut off any</i>

00:18.451 --> 00:19.985
<i>communication with Ellen.</i>

00:20.053 --> 00:21.922
<i>Whatever Ellen told</i>

00:21.990 --> 00:24.626
<i>you, she was covering up for me.</i>

00:24.694 --> 00:25.661
<i>When you left, I</i>

00:25.729 --> 00:26.796
<i>thought you were getting out of</i>

00:26.864 --> 00:27.597
<i>the business.</i>

00:27.665 --> 00:28.365
<i>This is my job,</i>

00:28.433 --> 00:29.366
<i>Dad.</i>

00:29.434 --> 00:30.735
<i>The Tobins... they're clients.</i>

00:30.803 --> 00:31.837
<i>There's money, and I</i>

00:31.905 --> 00:32.839
<i>want in.</i>

00:32.906 --> 00:33.607
<i>Your mother said you</i>

00:33.674 --> 00:34.541
<i>were helping transfer money to a</i>

00:34.608 --> 00:35.541
<i>charity?</i>

00:35.609 --> 00:36.209
<i>Yes.</i>

00:36.277 --> 00:36.876
<i>Do you remember</i>

00:36.944 --> 00:37.711
<i>anything about that form?</i>

00:37.778 --> 00:38.645
<i>I signed it so many</i>

00:38.713 --> 00:39.713
<i>times, but it was just a bunch</i>

00:39.780 --> 00:40.380
<i>of numbers.</i>

00:40.447 --> 00:41.147
<i>How would you feel</i>

00:41.215 --> 00:41.914
<i>about going back down to</i>

00:41.982 --> 00:42.915
<i>Antigua?</i>

00:42.983 --> 00:43.750
<i>Tessa Marchetti</i>

00:43.817 --> 00:45.252
<i>doesn't know anything, and she's</i>

00:45.320 --> 00:46.254
<i>on your side.</i>

00:46.321 --> 00:47.489
<i>You're sure of that how?</i>

00:47.556 --> 00:48.323
<i>Your father has</i>

00:48.391 --> 00:49.592
<i>supported Tessa her whole life.</i>

00:49.659 --> 00:50.594
<i>She's a problem.</i>

00:50.661 --> 00:51.262
<i>You have to</i>

00:51.329 --> 00:52.263
<i>intervene.</i>

00:52.331 --> 00:53.464
<i>Joe needs to know Tessa is his</i>

00:53.532 --> 00:54.465
<i>daughter.</i>

00:54.533 --> 00:55.199
<i>Did you tell him?</i>

00:55.267 --> 00:56.000
<i>Yes.</i>

00:56.068 --> 00:57.368
<i>Joe is going to leave Tessa</i>

00:57.435 --> 00:58.502
<i>alone.</i>

00:58.569 --> 01:01.530
<i>No, please, no.</i>

01:01.598 --> 01:05.032
<i>You had no choice.</i>

