02:01.805 --> 02:04.131
<i>Ms. Hewes?</i>

02:10.191 --> 02:12.125
<i>Yeah.</i>

02:12.192 --> 02:13.359
<i>Judge Reilly is here to see</i>

02:13.427 --> 02:14.360
<i>you.</i>

02:14.427 --> 02:16.294
<i>I'm very sorry to</i>

02:16.362 --> 02:17.929
<i>hear about Tessa Marchetti.</i>

02:17.997 --> 02:18.930
<i>Our investigator was</i>

02:18.998 --> 02:20.331
<i>killed with her.</i>

02:20.399 --> 02:21.632
<i>The cleaning staff at the hotel</i>

02:21.700 --> 02:22.633
<i>found them.</i>

02:22.701 --> 02:23.567
<i>We're obviously</i>

02:23.635 --> 02:24.501
<i>getting close to the money, Your</i>

02:24.569 --> 02:25.602
<i>Honor.</i>

02:25.670 --> 02:27.037
<i>If you take us off this case</i>

02:27.105 --> 02:29.905
<i>now, all the progress we've made</i>

02:29.973 --> 02:33.608
<i>would be for nothing.</i>

02:33.676 --> 02:35.276
<i>I reviewed your</i>

02:35.344 --> 02:36.777
<i>brief.</i>

02:36.845 --> 02:38.145
<i>You believe Miss Marchetti was</i>

02:38.213 --> 02:39.713
<i>transferring funds from a bank</i>

02:39.781 --> 02:41.447
<i>in Antigua to a charity in the</i>

02:41.515 --> 02:42.448
<i>U.S.</i>

02:42.516 --> 02:43.249
<i>That's how the Tobins</i>

02:43.316 --> 02:45.951
<i>were laundering their money.</i>

02:48.754 --> 02:51.155
<i>I'm going to let you</i>

02:51.223 --> 02:52.423
<i>see this through.</i>

02:52.490 --> 02:53.457
<i>Thank you,</i>

02:53.524 --> 02:54.457
<i>Your Honor.</i>

02:54.525 --> 02:55.492
<i>I promise you, you</i>

02:55.559 --> 02:57.560
<i>will not regret that decision.</i>

02:57.628 --> 02:58.861
<i>I hope so, Mr.</i>

02:58.929 --> 03:00.862
<i>Shayes.</i>

03:00.930 --> 03:02.397
<i>Patty, can I talk to you alone?</i>

03:02.465 --> 03:06.067
<i>Of course.</i>

03:06.134 --> 03:07.734
<i>All</i>

03:07.802 --> 03:12.304
<i>right, thank you very much.</i>

03:12.372 --> 03:13.972
<i>I recently received</i>

03:14.040 --> 03:15.373
<i>some information about Mr.</i>

03:15.441 --> 03:17.809
<i>Shayes.</i>

03:26.516 --> 03:28.517
<i>I assume you didn't</i>

03:28.585 --> 03:31.586
<i>know about this.</i>

03:35.590 --> 03:39.258
<i>I had no idea.</i>

